thread.title: Annie Longmore
thread.title_full: Ink Station reviewed by Annie Longmore

author: Annie Longmore
title: Annie Longmore
text: Inkstation is so convenient as I live in rural Australia. I place the order, it arrives within 2 to 3 working days. I save myself the time, the hassle of driving for an hour each way to get what I want, the cost of petrol and of course, I save on the products as well. I fully appreciate this great service
